宋体; white-space: normal; border-top-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(139,69,19); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">为何要佩戴蓝牙耳机</div>\r\n<p style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; padding-left: 0px; outline-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://pic.kuaishubao.com/picdata/goods/9/a/A250015586629_xt_2.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; padding-left: 0px; outline-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"goods-content-title\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(204,204,204) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 5px; border-right-width: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 5px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; padding-left: 0px; outline-width: 0px; width: 773px; padding-right: 0px; font: bold 18px/24px 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; border-top-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(139,69,19); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">模特展示</div>\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://pic.kuaishubao.com/picdata/goods/9/a/A250015586629_xt_6.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; display: inline-block; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; padding-left: 0px; outline-width: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"goods-content-title\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(204,204,204) 1px dotted; padding-bottom: 5px; border-right-width: 0px; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 30px 0px 5px; outline-style: none; outline-color: invert; padding-left: 0px; outline-width: 0px; width: 773px; padding-right: 0px; font: bold 18px/24px 微软雅黑, 宋体; white-space: normal; border-top-width: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(139,69,19); border-left-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">蓝牙耳机相关知识</div>\r\n<p><b style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: bold 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">蓝牙技术：</b><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 蓝牙版本市面上有V2.0/2.1/3.0/4.0，应用在蓝牙耳机时也有所差异。v2.1不仅多了支持立体声音效，在稳定度及效果上也有较好的表现。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 蓝牙耳机在规格上，有Handfree Profile（HFP）和Headset Profile（HSP）两大派别，决定耳机与手机的兼容性。前者意指免提功能、后者代表耳机功能。其中HFP格式的蓝牙耳机支持手机可以同时在耳机上操作手机设定好的重拨、来电保留、来电拒听等免提选项功能。目前大部分机型是同时支持HFP与HSP。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 蓝牙耳机结构相对复杂，而且非常讲究讲究技术含量。决定蓝牙耳机品质的因素有很多，包括芯片、电池、内部其他部件，还有机体设计、外壳用料、成型工艺等。到了今天，蓝牙耳机已经跟手机等随身器械一样，是集功能和个性品味一体的常用工具。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<b style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: bold 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">蓝牙耳机核心的部件有：</b><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 主芯片：其决定蓝牙耳机整体综合性能的实现。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 电池：供电。保护板的品质及保护电路的设计关乎耳机的使用寿命。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 喇叭：其品质的好坏直接影响到耳朵听觉的效果。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 咪头：音源传送为其功能的体现,咪头的正确选用也会影响到音质。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 天线：目前为板材天线所代替,但是个别受体积所限制的耳机仍需要采用贴片专用陶瓷天线,合理的选用及调校将直接影响到通话距离。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 晶振：提供频率震荡，影响射频。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 滤波器：滤波，将2.441-2.480以外频率滤除掉。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 存储IC：也叫EEPROM，存放资料</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<b style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: bold 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">芯片主要方案商及特征:</b><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; CSR （英国）目前全球一流的蓝牙方案供应商。其优点主要表现在：抑制噪音能力强、功耗低（延长电池使用时间）、性能稳定、技术超前、成本略高。目前为诺基亚、IBM、摩托罗拉以及索尼爱立信等蓝牙方案的主要提供商。&nbsp;</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Broadcom（美国）Broadcom蓝牙耳机方案具备先进噪声消除技术，方案更多的被采用于笔记本、手机内置模块，其对于生产工艺要求较高。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; ISSC（台湾）后起的蓝牙方案之秀，其方案主要被采用于蓝牙耳机、蓝牙适配器，价钱便宜，但其技术开发一直跟随着CSR。蓝牙与蓝牙设备之间的有效使用距离方面表现突出。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 力源（台湾）蓝牙方案的后起之秀，其方案主要被采用于蓝牙耳机、蓝牙适配器。价钱便宜，但是综合性能较差，多被应用于高仿机及低端机市场。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 捷顶微（上海）首个国产蓝牙方案，于2008年上市，但是由于综合性能很较差，目前在市场极少被制造厂家所采用。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<b style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: bold 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">蓝牙耳机使用距离:</b><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 蓝牙耳机的传输距离，这与蓝牙版本无关，而取决于蓝牙技术PowerClass。现在大部分手机与移动装置所使用的是PowerClassⅡ，标准传输距离10米&middot;；而升级的PowerClass ClassⅠ则是将传输距离提升到100米，两种版本都能支持A2DP立体声传输协议，可与立体声耳机互联。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一般而言，蓝牙耳机的使用距离在10米左右。当使用环境为空旷平地时，蓝牙设备的使用距离可以达到更远，如浦诺菲PBH-A380蓝牙耳机在空旷平地正常使用的直线距离可达到50米。当然，这个还需要处决于手机的蓝牙模块功率，因为蓝牙是交互类信号，如果某手机的蓝牙模块只能发送到3米，那么蓝牙耳机也只能3米内与该手机连接。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<b style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: bold 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">蓝牙耳机接听电话和播放音乐:</b><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 在选用蓝牙耳机之前首先要确认手机自身是否支持蓝牙功能，基本上所有带蓝牙功能的手机都能使用蓝牙耳机接听电话。对于播放音乐方面，立体声耳机支持A2PD协议，能兼容绝大部分手机的音乐播功能。有少部分诺基亚老型号的手机和部分国产功能机也可以通过单声道耳机播放音乐，但音质不理想，所以建议需要音乐播放功能的顾客选购立体声蓝牙耳机。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">pivoFUL浦诺菲教您怎么选属于自己的蓝牙</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<b style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: bold 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">怎么样选购蓝牙耳机？</b><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1、所谓看菜吃饭，量体裁衣。选蓝牙耳机其实就跟买衣服一样，首先得看自身所需；买蓝牙耳机先考虑自己的目的。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 如果您经常需要驾驶或者长期在工场指挥作业，只是行车方便或者因为工作的繁多而需要解脱双手让自己在繁忙中还能便捷的接听电话的话，尽量选购单声道的蓝牙耳机；尤其是免耳挂类的蓝牙耳机更为实用，如浦诺菲的PBH-A118C单声道蓝牙、PBH-A130单声道蓝牙等。（按所需，适而用&mdash;&mdash;经济实在）</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 假如您还希在休息的时间或者某些可放松的场合下倾听几首音乐，调节下心情什么的话，您可以选购单双声道通用（单转双）的蓝牙耳机，如浦诺菲的PBH-260S。在行车或者作业的场合只需佩带主耳机，轻松自在的电话交谈；午间休息或者饭前茶后配上副耳机，轻松享受片刻自在的生活乐章。（有所需，适可选&mdash;&mdash;灵动适中）</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 假如您是一个音乐发烧友，最好的建议就是购买高档的有线耳机，因为蓝牙无论做得怎么优秀，经过无线信号的传播衰减，音质肯定会有所下降；但如果您的确被有线耳机各种碍手碍脚拖累得烦了，又或者想尝试一下更加自在的享受高品质的音乐，那么您一定要选购高端的纯立体声蓝牙耳机。如浦诺菲的PBH-A360立体声蓝牙耳机、PBH-A550S立体声蓝牙耳机。音质跟高档有线耳机相差无几，尤其是A550S极品立体声蓝牙，外观清新唯美、音质纯正、做工精湛细腻，集功能品位与一体。（因所需，尽所选&mdash;&mdash;极品追求）</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 假如您是一位繁忙的业务人事，你不止佩戴一台手机，希望在行车或者繁忙的工作生活中解放双手接听电话，那么您最好选购双待机蓝牙耳机；能够同时连接两台手机待机并有选择的接听电话。如浦诺菲的（有特需，有特用&mdash;&mdash;特有所用）</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 倘若您是有了一定基础的商务人事，繁忙的工作会议、频密的社交应酬，一方面需要在工作和应酬过程中解脱双手连线客户，另一方面也要体验出您不同的身份和品位，蓝牙耳机也必须是一种身份的匹配；在选择蓝牙的时候重点考虑蓝牙的设计、工艺，这样的您想必也没多少戴耳机来听音乐的时间，请尽量考虑高端的单声道蓝牙耳机。如pivoful的PBH-A218单声道蓝牙，与众不同的设计，精致细腻的做工；一拿到手就能体现到一种独特、高雅、简约而稳重感觉，起音质也比普通的单声道蓝牙耳机明显优越。（有品味，有品位&mdash;&mdash;身份象征）</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 如果您是一位年轻时尚而美女或者帅哥，或者蓝牙耳机也是你炫彩缤纷的生活装配，那么您还可以选购外观概念设计主导的蓝牙系列耳机，基本的功能齐备而有缤纷多彩，浦诺菲的PBH-A118C炫彩系列蓝牙、PBH-A129糖果系列蓝牙等，作为着装搭配、出行生活都是不错的选择。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 2、看蓝牙耳机品质。买东西看品质，这道理不需要解释。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 芯片：蓝牙耳机核心部件就是其蓝牙芯片，前面已经对蓝牙芯片商有作分析，首选CSR或者Broadcom芯片的蓝牙。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 电池：涉及到耳机的续航能力待机时间和耳机运行过程中的稳定性，所以在选购过程中可以适度关注耳机参数。</span><br style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 14px/21px Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 做工：工艺很重要，但只有拿上手的时候通过对比才能明显区分。手感质感、表面处理、衔接缝除的均匀程度、细腻修边处的毛胚等都是区分工艺的要素。产品的实物拍摄图片展示能辅助您区分产品的工艺。蓝牙的品质还与其内部板材、天线、滤波器、等很多因素相关，但作为消费者并不易区分得那么细致。但是，&ldquo;不怕不识货，就怕货比货。&rdquo;很多不同的产品，一校对就能有感觉了。</span></p>', 'images/201507/thumb_img/2394_thumb_G_1436087437466.jpg', 'images/201507/goods_img/2394_G_1436087437864.jpg', 'images/201507/source_img/2394_G_1436087437158.png', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1389779212', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1389787255', '0', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '0', '', '', '', '');
